      <title>Re: 4.4 error?</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/ca_glossary/forum/general/4_4_error/re_4_4_error2</link>
      <description>Also, I wanted to change a little bit the functionality, because i want when a user clicks the item to be sent to the item page where he can find further explanations:&#13;
&#13;
Remove:&#13;
&lt;code&gt;$glossaryUrl = $glossaryNode-&gt;attribute('url_alias');&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
&#13;
After&#13;
&lt;code&gt;$title = $dataMap[$titleAttributeIdentifier]-&gt;content();&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
Add&#13;
&lt;code&gt;$url = $definition-&gt;url();&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
&#13;
Replace&#13;
&lt;code&gt;$tpl-&gt;setVariable( 'glossaryUrl', $glossaryUrl );&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
to&#13;
&lt;code&gt;$tpl-&gt;setVariable( 'url', $url );&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
&#13;
open &lt;b&gt;design/standard/templates/ca_glossary.tpl&lt;/b&gt;&#13;
replace&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&lt;a class="ca_glossary" href={concat($glossaryUrl,'#',$title)|ezurl}&gt;{$title|downcase}&lt;span&gt;{$definition}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
with&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&lt;a class="ca_glossary" href={concat($url)|ezurl}&gt;{$title|downcase}&lt;span&gt;{$definition}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/code&gt;</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Sao Tavi)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/ca_glossary/forum/general/4_4_error/re_4_4_error2</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Nov 2010 14:27:25 +0000</pubDate>
