      <title>Re: 4.4 error?</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/ca_glossary/forum/general/4_4_error/re_4_4_error</link>
      <description>Also, I had to change    &#13;
     &#13;
&lt;code&gt;       $regExp = "/\b(".implode('|',$matchArray).")\b(?!.*&lt;\/(".$exceptionTagsString.")&gt;+)(?![^(&gt;|&lt;)]*&gt;+)/i";&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
to&lt;code&gt;$regExp = "/\b(".implode('|',$matchArray).")\b(?![^(&gt;|&lt;)]*&gt;+)/i";&lt;/code&gt; (I am not good with regex sintax, but it did not work with the initial version).&#13;
&#13;
&#13;
and&#13;
&lt;code&gt;            $definition = $dataMap[$definitionAttributeIdentifier]-&gt;content();&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
to&#13;
&lt;code&gt;            $definition_obj = $dataMap[$definitionAttributeIdentifier]-&gt;content();&#13;
			$definition = $definition_obj-&gt;XMLData;&lt;/code&gt;</description>
